			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Waste tires, also known as 'black pollution', are difficult to degrade. The safe handling and recycling of waste tires have always been a focus and challenge for the global rubber industry. Pyrolysis can not only solve the problem of environmental pollution but also completely treat the waste tires and recover valuable materials. Waste tire management fees are often collected with sales tax returns. The waste tire recycling program is effective in managing waste tires generated in Utah due to the coordinated efforts of all stakeholders</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">废旧轮胎，又称“黑色污染”，难以降解。废旧轮胎的安全处理和回收一直是全球橡胶行业关注的焦点和挑战。热解不仅可以解决环境污染问题，还可以彻底处理废旧轮胎并回收有价值的材料。废旧轮胎管理费通常与销售税申报表一起收取。由于所有利益相关者的协调努力，废轮胎回收计划在管理犹他州产生的废轮胎方面是有效的。</common:generalComment>
